trigger

public void trigger()
Triggers the callback request that contacts the Sponsorpay Advertiser API. If and when a successful response is received from the server, the AdvertiserCallbackSender.APIResultListener registered through the constructor AdvertiserCallbackSender(SPCredentials, APIResultListener) will be notified.
